title: Where is Santa? Journey to Lapland to Find Him (2002) Documentary

sources.title: Where is Santa? Journey to Lapland to Find Him (2002) Documentary
sources.description:
Journey through the history of this merry man known the world over as Father Christmas; the traditions of this Christian Festival over the centuries and finally onto the real search through Lapland via sledge, snowmobile and even reindeer sleighs.

Director & Narrator: Liam Dale
Genres: Christmas, Documentary
